%H A055441 <a href="/index/Be#Benford">Index entries for sequences related to Benford's law</a>.
%e A055441 a(50) = 2 so that after 50 terms we have had 15 1's, 9 2's, 6 3's, 5 4's, 4 5's, 3 6's, 3 7's, 3 8's and 2 9's.
